    "RecordEnvelope": {
      "description": "Fields shared by every record kind.\n\nField order is fixed by the struct declaration; serde derives produce a deterministic key order in `serde_json`'s output, which underpins the canonical-JSON hashing performed by [`crate::hash::state_hash`].",
